What A Day!!!!!! Liquor Run Premiere

Wow where do we start? 15 mins of The Red Carpet Premiere of @liquorrunthemovie produced by the @hallmillsnetwork @principalmills @cgrimwhit and directed by @directorjhall . 

Your 15mins of #footage includes two different audios, one from a lapel microphone, and one from a boom mic. We apologize for the variety of audio and all its glory and not so glory but @cityplex12_ was packed, loud and a zoo. Hard to hear what the Cast & Crew were saying at times, so we needed some backup. Thanks to @redimprinttv we got just that. 

We ask the cast & crew about their role, what their copping from the LQ before it closes, and who was the funniest on set? 

Thank you @iamhassanoliver @bigmommabadass2012 @billionairecomedy06 @hollywooddevon @iamstevenstrickland @triniladylex @slimsuliart_world @ms_motivated_angel_lee @wtf_foodtruck @mikerosscomedy @courlione @verry_richmon @iamjaedylan and many others for a being a part of the footage.

It’s a lot going on in this footage don’t miss it. Lots of jokes. Lots of the funny. A lotta gems being dropped too.
